It seems that this is the sphere that the Messenger needed. Exchange it for one of the ones you need шкатулок: астеризовую, адамасовую, бриллиантовую или бирмитовую.

A transparent petal made of the finest rock crystal, made by the best glassblowers. Rumor has it,  that one petal brings good luck, and if someone is lucky enough to collect seven petals of different colors, he can combine them into tsvetik-semitsvetik and get a reward: Pocket by Yar Marko,  Fragment of Nimelin x5, A ghostly tablet, Rubidium plate x100 and Ark with flying pollen x300. In order to fully accommodate the entire reward, you will need 4 slots in my backpack.  

You can sell the petal, exchange it with your friends, or собрать цветики-семицветики, цветики-букетики и flower baskets and get the royal reward!

For every five levels of your character, you get an additional 1 petal of the same color!

Any technomage can become the owner of a petal 5 level level, which one is valid during the promotion period"Multi-colored week #will make at least one payment in the amount of at least 70 crystals. Regardless of the number and size of payments, per share is a petal (or petals, if the player's level is greater than 9) is given to the participants only once! ! Details

## here.####

Colorful bouquet of seven flowers. The delicate aroma of the bouquet will give more than one day of good mood to its owner.

If собрать корзину из семи such bouquets, as a reward, you can get: Amber bead X300, Stoletova bead X300, Malachite bead x300,  Chrome Ore x1000, Tungsten Ore x1000, Palladium ore x1000, Stone of the universe x300, Ark with flying pollen x70000 and
